', '  \end{flushright} \vspace{2cm}
', '
', '
', '  \item The circle $O$ is shown below with diameter $\overline{AOC}$ and radius $\overline{BO}$. Given $m\angle BAO = 73^\circ$. Find the measure of the central angle $\angle AOB$.
', '  \begin{flushright}
