', '      \draw [fill] (-4,0.4) circle [radius=0.05] node[above]{$R$};
', '    \end{tikzpicture}
', '
', '
', '\item Given $m \angle 1 = 4x+6$, $m \angle 2 = 6x-32$. Find $m \angle 1$.
', '    \begin{tikzpicture}[scale=.3, rotate=15]
