', '\newpage
', '\subsubsection*{Classwork: Estimating and measuring angles, length, and area} 
', '  \item Find the area of a semi-circle with diameter of 6 centimeters.
', '   \begin{flushright}
', '    \begin{tikzpicture}[scale=.635]
', '      %\draw [help lines] (-5,-1) grid (5,4);
